    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak. At its heart is the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and a linear torque curve. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to mitigate structural fatigue. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock for precise corner-exit traction. This vehicle retains its factory-applied finish with no signs of environmental degradation. Every bushing, mount, and dampening component remains within factory tolerances, providing the tactile, communicative steering feedback synonymous with the marque. A rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically flawless specimen with a fully documented service history.",
